	"content": "<h1 class=\"page-title\">Week 3</h1>\n  \n  <div id=\"todo-date-mount-point\"></div>\n  \n    <p><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Overview</span></strong></p>\n<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 1\">\n<div class=\"section\" style=\"background-color: rgb(100.000000%, 100.000000%, 100.000000%);\">\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\n<div class=\"column\">\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'NimbusSanL';\">Financial intermediaries (banks/credit unions, investment banks, investment companies), security issuance process (private firms staying private or going public, public firms), mechanics of trading (brokers and dealers, trading costs, buying on margin, selling securities short), regulation of securities markets (government vs self-regulation, Sarbanes-Oxley Act, insider trading)<br></span></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Learning Objectives</span></strong></p>\n<p>Upon completion of this week, you will be able to understand:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>how different types of financial intermediaries allocate capital</li>\n<li>mutual fund fee structure</li>\n<li>how firms raise capital in private offerings vs public markets</li>\n<li>the mechanics of trading securities</li>\n<li>investor protection in the US</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Preparation for class</span></strong></p>\n<p>Mandatory reading:</p>\n<p>Lecture 2: <span class=\"instructure_file_holder link_holder instructure_file_link_holder\"><a id=\"80590984\" class=\"inline_disabled preview_in_overlay\" title=\"Link\" href=\"https://canvas.colorado.edu/courses/123249/files/80590984?wrap=1\" target=\"_blank\" data-canvas-previewable=\"true\" data-api-endpoint=\"https://canvas.colorado.edu/api/v1/courses/123249/files/80590984\" data-api-returntype=\"File\">lecture 2.pdf</a><a class=\"file_download_btn\" role=\"button\" download=\"\" style=\"margin-inline-start: 5px; text-decoration: none;\" href=\"https://canvas.colorado.edu/courses/123249/files/80590984/download?download_frd=1\"><span role=\"presentation\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 1920 1920\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" style=\"width:1em; height:1em; vertical-align:middle; fill:currentColor\">\n    <path d=\"m1807.093 1482.477 79.736 79.963-355.313 355.312H355.346L.035 1562.44l79.85-79.963 322.22 322.334H1484.76l322.334-322.334ZM997.677-.033v1167.02l355.313-355.313 79.962 79.85-491.858 491.633L449.46 891.524l79.962-79.85 355.313 355.313V-.033h112.941Z\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><span class=\"screenreader-only\">Download lecture 2.pdf</span></a></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Class</span></strong></p>\n<p>Class zoom link: <a title=\"Class logistics\" href=\"https://canvas.colorado.edu/courses/123249/pages/class-logistics\" data-course-type=\"wikiPages\" data-published=\"true\" data-api-endpoint=\"https://canvas.colorado.edu/api/v1/courses/123249/pages/class-logistics\" data-api-returntype=\"Page\">Class logistics</a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span class=\"instructure_file_holder link_holder instructure_file_link_holder\">Assignments and Quizzes</span></strong></span></p>\n<p><a title=\"A1\" href=\"https://canvas.colorado.edu/courses/123249/assignments/2494202\" data-course-type=\"assignments\" data-published=\"true\" data-api-endpoint=\"https://canvas.colorado.edu/api/v1/courses/123249/assignments/2494202\" data-api-returntype=\"Assignment\">A1</a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>Additional Resources</strong></span></p>\n<p>Chapters 3 and 4</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>Class Notes</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Sep 2 class recording:</span>&nbsp;</p>\n<div style=\"margin: 6px 0;\"><a style=\"color: #0d6bde; text-decoration: non